    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Spotted this just now, but with a different replication path... If you use: https://instantsearchjs.netlify.com/stories/?selectedKind=RefinementList&selectedStory=with%20show%20more&full=0&addons=1&stories=1&panelRight=0&addonPanel=storybook%2Factions%2Factions-panel\r\n\r\n- Observe the filter limit is 3\r\n- Click show more\r\n- enter enough chars into the search box to reduce filters, e.g. `samsungasd`\r\n\r\nYou will see `Show less` remains even though only 3 filters are present\r\n\r\nThis is my +1 ... hopefully someone can fix this soon :)",
